race.comment: The penny has dropped for BRAVE MONARCH (2) who has strung back-to-back wins together and is racing with a lot of confidence. Is one from one over this seven-furlong journey and winning rider Harley sticks in the saddle. Can bring up the hat-trick. The well-related ANOTHER CASHIE (5) (full to G3 winner Shangri La Spring) has been right there in all three starts to date including shedding the maiden tag at Grafton two back. Only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a role in the finish. PROVOKER (4) got a well-deserved victory last time out and will have come on with that win now under the belt. Has to be included. HA'PENNY HATCH (3) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top-five in eight of nine career outings. A must for the multiples. RED CODE (7) next in line from the favourable draw.
